public class FeaturePredicate
extends SequenceFeaturePredicate

Author:
jaschasilbermann

Adds no new functionality to the Sequence Feature Predicate, but constrains tyhe entire query to Sequence Features.

This should give a performance improvement over using a Sequence Feature Predicate with clazz = FeaturePredicate.class .
